{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Mental health first aiders should be a legal requirement in any workplace.",
        "additional_details": "\" A staggering 70 million work days are lost each year due to mental health problems in the UK\" according to the mental health foundation.",
        "background": "For many people, most of their time is spent in the workplace and this can bring pressure upon them. If first aid is a legal requirement in the work place, then let's amend the \"The Health and Safety (First-Aid) Regulations 1981\" to include the ever growing problem of mental health.",
